These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, avocado, spinach, carrot
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, canadian, indian, argentine
1. the canadian is on the left of the colombian##1
2. the person eating broccoli is the argentine##1
3. the indian is on the right of the colombian##1
4. the person eating avocado is on the left of the argentine##1
5. the person eating carrot is on the left of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | carrot | spinach | avocado | broccoli   |
| Nationality   | canadian  | colombian     | indian   | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, writing, chess, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, baseball, rowing
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | chess | skydiving | writing | baking    |
| Sport   | baseball    | golf      | biathlon | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, chess, hiking, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, horror, comedy, spy
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person watching musical movies##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | skydiving | hiking   | chess |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | comedy | spy | horror         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, musical, horror, comedy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, cricket, soccer, handball
1. the person who's sport is cricket is the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | musical | zombie  | horror      |
| Sport         | cricket | handball   | soccer | lacrosse |

