.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, garlic, strawberry, tomato
4 different pets are kept: goat, snake, mouse, chinchilla
1. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person eating tomato is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | tomato | strawberry | garlic | grapes |
| Pet    | goat       | chinchilla | mouse | snake     |

