2. the german is on the left of the indonesian##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the indonesian##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | german | indonesian | argentine | spanish |
| Pet           | goat      | pony | lizard | rat    |

