2. the fan of country is on the far right##1
3. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1
5. the fan of blues is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | disco | blues | pop | country  |
| Pet           | fish | frog | hamster       | snake |

