.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, engineer, dancer, analyst
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, motorbike, snowmobile, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the engineer##1
2. the person driving the taxi is the analyst##1
3. the engineer is on the right of the security-guard##1
4. the dancer is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the van is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | dancer | security-guard      | engineer | analyst |
| Transport   | van          | motorbike | snowmobile     | taxi    |

