.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, 7up, lemonade
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, motorbike, scooter, jet-ski
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | iced-tea | 7up  | mirinda | lemonade |
| Transport   | jet-ski | scooter | motorbike          | van    |

