3. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | photography | hiking | fishing | magic-tricks |
