.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, polish, indonesian, spanish
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, airplane
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the polish##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the chinese is on the left of the indonesian##1
4. the spanish is the person driving the airplane##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | chinese | indonesian | polish | spanish   |
| Transport     | roller  | helicopter    | motorbike       | airplane |

 